item.title: About
item.description: Hello! My name is M Haris Mir. I am a data enthusiest, certified Data Analyst, and an aspiring Data Scientist. As a lifelong learner, I am passionate about staying at the forefront of emerging trends and technologies in data science. I believe that data analytics has the power to transform industries and create positive societal impact. I aim to leverage my expertise in data analytics, engineering management, and problem-solving to tackle complex challenges and drive innovation.
